Populate Date Columns

Source: R/populateDateColumns.r
dateFuncs.Rd

Creates various date columns for WRTDS study.

populateDateColumns(rawData)

decimalDate(rawData)

Arguments

rawData

vector with dateTime

Value

DateFrame dataframe

Examples

dateTime <- c('1984-02-28 13:56', '1984-03-01 00:00', '1986-03-01 00:00',"1986-10-15 00:00")
expandedDateDF <- populateDateColumns(dateTime)
dateTime <- c('1984-02-28', '1984-03-01', '1986-03-01',"1986-10-15")
expandedDateDF <- populateDateColumns(dateTime)
dateTime <- c('1984-02-28 13:56', '1984-03-01 00:00', '1986-03-01 00:00',"1986-10-15 00:00")
decimalDate(dateTime)
#> [1] 1984.160 1984.164 1986.162 1986.786
